When using MVC you have to couple some business logic into the html

These frameworks are JavaScript frameworks that facilitate the clear separation
of the “frontend” or the data rendering logic from the “backend”
which is typically just a REST based API that loads and processes data through a resource model.

The frontend should dictate how the data is rendered while backend processes the data